channel.description:
Comes in handy for repacking broken NPC models or Object models. Have fun.

NPCs:
[code=java]		 public static void dumpModels() {
                         int id = 1;
			  EntityDef npc = EntityDef.forID(id); 
			  System.out.println(npc.name);
			  if(npc.anIntArray94 != null) {
			   for(int modelid = 0; modelid < npc.anIntArray94.length; modelid++) {
			    System.out.println(npc.anIntArray94[modelid]);
			   }
			  }
			 }[/code]

